{
  "info": {
    "name": "Estimator API",
    "description": "Collection for testing the Estimator API endpoints. This API provides project estimation capabilities using AI agents.\n\n## Environment Variables\n- `API_BASE_URL`: Base URL for the API (default: http://localhost:3000)\n\n## Sample Projects\n- **sample-project**: E-Commerce Platform (React/NestJS)\n- **python-fastapi-project**: Task Management SaaS (Python/FastAPI)\n- **java-springboot-project**: Healthcare Patient Portal (Java/Spring Boot)\n- **go-microservices-project**: Real-time Analytics Platform (Go)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "variable": [
    {
      "key": "API_BASE_URL",
      "value": "http://localhost:3000",
      "type": "string"
    },
    {
      "key": "job_id",
      "value": "",
      "type": "string"
    }
  ],
  "auth": {
    "type": "noauth"
  },
